  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0db6\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0db8\u0dca \u0daf\u0db8\u0dbd \u0d9c\u0dc4\u0dbd \u0dba\u0dcf \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"If you can't do it, you should go to Tamil Nadu.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gampaha District Councilor Mr. Sarath Fonseka said in the Parliament today 6 that if the opposition gets the mandate to form the government, it should take the government without fear and if it cannot hold its neck, then it should go away.",
        "Mr. Fonseka said that if the government is displeased with the people, if the people are asking the government to go home, if the people are lining up to oust the government and the president, then the opposition should definitely get that mandate.",
        "Mr. Fonseka said that he does not think that an all-party government can be formed from the opposition and that it will not get 113."
      ],
